		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Jewish ritual bath</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Mikva" redirects here. For the U.S. Representative and federal judge, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abner_J._Mikva" class="mw-redirect" title="Abner J. Mikva">Abner J. Mikva</a>.</div>
